      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "URANA XAVIER (6) jumped from a middle draw last time and could manage only fourth and beaten 3.5 lengths (30.27) at this track. Has a good record here at this journey. Rates on top in this line up. SPRING MILES (8) had been racing well prior to his last start seventh at this track following a Grade 5 win three back with a third placing. Expected to do much better this time. WHISPERED (7) has been out of the placings at her last two outings but shapes well for this if she can recapture her flying win a few runs back, getting around Sandown over 515m in 29.34. Expected to feature on best figures. PAW RAYNOR (3) is last start winner who looks one of the chances.",
